From a7376f3b2e282b0adc31146ba741fc51f17a3c3d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tim 'mithro' Ansell <me@mith.ro>
Date: Mon, 6 Apr 2026 12:18:59 +0930
Subject: [PATCH 05/16] Wire BCM2838 peripherals: GENET, PCIe, RNG200, Thermal

Integration commit: connect all new devices to the BCM2838 SoC
and RPi 4B machine.

- bcm2838_peripherals.h: Add includes and device state fields
- bcm2838_peripherals.c: Init/realize for all 4 new devices with
  memory mapping and IRQ wiring
- bcm2838.c: Connect device IRQs to GIC (SPI 125, 143, 157-158)
- raspi4b.c: Remove DTB disabling of now-implemented devices
- meson.build: Add new source files to build
- trace-events: Add RNG200 trace events
- raspi.rst: Move GENET/PCIe to implemented, PWM only missing

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
